Library doca-cpp requires NVIDIA DOCA SDK v3.2.0 installation
and was tested only on Linux Ubuntu 24.04 Kernel 6.8.0-31

Library doca-cpp provides CMake targets:

    find_package(doca-cpp CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE doca-cpp::doca-cpp)

For direct header inclusion:

    #include <doca-cpp/core/device.hpp>
